{"type":"message","id":"0d464c62","parentId":"a94af2c9","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:03.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to execute a cron task for real-time stock price monitoring. I need to read the configuration file at ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md to understand what tasks are required.\n\nLet me read that file first to understand what needs to be done.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_839daa8975bf44aea5c2bde8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773125100100}}
{"type":"message","id":"61303819","parentId":"0d464c62","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:03.022Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_839daa8975bf44aea5c2bde8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 你的工作路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n- 自定义文件路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock\n- 你独享的skill存放位置：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/skills\n- 以下描述中没有具体位置的文件都是自定义文件，存放在自定义路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 指定了具体路径的文件，按照指定路径读取，如：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md；\n- 如果你需要新建文件，统一存放在自定义路径下；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘或休市，未收盘或休市，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、阅读~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md内的skill使用说明，严格按照要求使用skill；\n4、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时日线数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n5、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n6、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n7、读取receiver-list.txt接受者用户列表文件，使用命令openclaw message broadcast --channel feishu --account stock --targets <user_id1> --targets <user_id2>... --message <xxx>，\n   将预警数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给列表文件中的用户；\n   - --targets <user_id> 参数可重复\n8、推送数据格式严格按照alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125103019}}
{"type":"message","id":"a80f26d2","parentId":"61303819","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:11.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to read several related files to understand the full task:\n1. TOOLS.md - for skill usage instructions\n2. get-data-template.md - for data format requirements\n3. alert-rules.md - for alert rules\n4. receiver-list.txt - for recipient list\n5. alert-template.md - for message template\n\nLet me read these files to understand the complete requirements.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9d3acc9d1886411fb7547981","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1e45a9490ca848ae85f1f674","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0f84194f2e4243a09bc95daf","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5a01ca0ea6864b12aa1acc16","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_26a92af57e684d819d4d49e2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773125103022}}
{"type":"message","id":"5fc188e3","parentId":"a80f26d2","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:11.831Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9d3acc9d1886411fb7547981","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/TOOLS.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125111830}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf05e812","parentId":"5fc188e3","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:11.834Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1e45a9490ca848ae85f1f674","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额 - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价\n- 今开价\n- 最高价\n- 最低价\n- 成交量\n- 成交额\n- 市盈率\n- 总市值\n- 换手率\n\n【计算规则】\n- 涨跌额 = 当前股价 - 昨收价\n- 涨跌额 = (当前股价 - 昨收价) / 昨收价\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125111833}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a41e9e3","parentId":"bf05e812","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:11.837Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0f84194f2e4243a09bc95daf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125111836}}
{"type":"message","id":"69dbb40a","parentId":"2a41e9e3","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:11.842Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5a01ca0ea6864b12aa1acc16","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\nou_0737da20bef21e4dff04d2b83f927208\nou_144623d3a3b4a119305355db7813bb31\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125111840}}
{"type":"message","id":"185804de","parentId":"69dbb40a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:11.844Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_26a92af57e684d819d4d49e2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n**注意**：数据来源必须标明\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n\n【数据来源】\n数据来源：xxx\n更新时间：yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125111843}}
