{"type":"message","id":"8d0c0d32","parentId":"efdee671","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:30.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I have a clear picture. Let me understand the task flow:\n\n1. First, I need to check if the market is open using tushare-data skill (check trading day/market status)\n2. Clear realtime-data.txt if it has content\n3. Get real-time stock data for the watchlist stocks\n4. Filter based on alert rules:\n   - General: drop > 3% OR rise > 5%\n   - Special for 中国石油 (601857.SH): rise > 2% OR drop > 1%\n5. If there are alerts, send to feishu users from receiver-list.txt\n\nLooking at the current realtime-data.txt, I can see data is already there from 14:40. The current time is 14:45.\n\nLet me check if there's an existing script to check market status and fetch data. I see there's a check_market_status.py script. Let me also look at the existing scripts to understand the pattern.\n\nActually, looking at the flow, I should:\n1. Check market status first\n2. Clear the file\n3. Fetch fresh data\n4. Filter and alert\n\nLet me check the market status script and see if I can use existing scripts.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6264e9ff3b35439b80f61a53","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/check_market_status.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fdd0e5ddb5a14240ac15fae2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get_realtime_data.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773125119231}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d44ad11","parentId":"8d0c0d32","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:30.523Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6264e9ff3b35439b80f61a53","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n检查今日是否休市，并获取自选股实时日线数据\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 初始化 pro 接口\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\nprint(f\"Token: {token[:10]}...{token[-10:] if len(token) > 20 else token}\")\n\nif not token:\n    print(\"ERROR: TUSHARE_TOKEN 环境变量未设置\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 获取今天日期\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\ntoday_str = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\n\n# 检查交易日历（上交所）\ntry:\n    print(f\"检查交易日历：{today}\")\n    cal_df = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=today, end_date=today, is_open='1')\n    print(f\"交易日历返回：{cal_df}\")\n    if cal_df.empty:\n        print(f\"今日 ({today_str}) 休市，结束任务\")\n        sys.exit(0)\n    else:\n        print(f\"今日 ({today_str}) 正常交易，继续执行\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"检查交易日历出错：{e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n    sys.exit(1)\n\n# 读取自选股列表\nwatchlist_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt')\nstocks = []\ntry:\n    with open(watchlist_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        for line in f:\n            line = line.strip()\n            if line and '|' in line:\n                code, name = line.split('|', 1)\n                # 转换代码格式为 tushare 格式\n                if '.' not in code:\n                    if code.startswith('6') or code.startswith('9'):\n                        code = code + '.SH'\n                    else:\n                        code = code + '.SZ'\n                stocks.append(code)\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"读取自选股列表出错：{e}\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nif not stocks:\n    print(\"自选股列表为空\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nprint(f\"自选股数量：{len(stocks)}\")\nprint(f\"股票列表：{stocks}\")\n\n# 获取实时日线数据\ntry:\n    # 使用实时日线接口，一次性获取所有股票数据\n    ts_codes = ','.join(stocks)\n    print(f\"请求 tushare 实时日线数据：{ts_codes}\")\n    \n    # 使用实时日线接口 (doc_id=372)\n    df = pro.realtime_daily(ts_code=ts_codes)\n    \n    if df.empty:\n        print(\"未获取到实时数据\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    print(f\"获取到 {len(df)} 条数据\")\n    print(f\"列名：{df.columns.tolist()}\")\n    print(df)\n    \n    # 保存到 realtime-data.txt\n    output_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt')\n    df.to_csv(output_path, index=False, encoding='utf-8')\n    print(f\"数据已保存到：{output_path}\")\n    \nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"获取实时数据出错：{e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n    sys.exit(1)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125130522}}
{"type":"message","id":"a844cb00","parentId":"9d44ad11","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:30.527Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fdd0e5ddb5a14240ac15fae2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n从东方财富获取实时股价数据\n使用东方财富 API: https://quote.eastmoney.com/center/gridlist.html\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 读取自选股列表\nwatchlist_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt')\nstocks = []\nstock_names = {}\n\ntry:\n    with open(watchlist_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        for line in f:\n            line = line.strip()\n            if line and '|' in line:\n                code, name = line.split('|', 1)\n                stocks.append({'code': code, 'name': name})\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"读取自选股列表出错：{e}\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nif not stocks:\n    print(\"自选股列表为空\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nprint(f\"自选股数量：{len(stocks)}\")\n\n# 东方财富实时行情 API (每个股票单独请求)\n# https://push2.eastmoney.com/api/qt/stock/get\noutput_lines = []\nheader = \"代码，名称，当前价，涨跌额，涨跌幅，昨收，今开，最高，最低，成交量，成交额，时间\"\noutput_lines.append(header)\n\ncurrent_time = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n\nfor stock in stocks:\n    code = stock['code']\n    name = stock['name']\n    \n    # 转换代码格式\n    if '.HK' in code:\n        hk_code = code.replace('.HK', '')\n        secid = f\"120.{hk_code}\"\n    elif '.' in code:\n        secid = code\n    elif code.startswith('6') or code.startswith('9') or code.startswith('5'):\n        secid = f\"1.{code}\"\n    elif code.startswith('8') or code.startswith('4'):\n        secid = f\"1.{code}\"\n    else:\n        secid = f\"0.{code}\"\n    \n    # fields: f43=最新价，f44=涨跌额，f170=涨跌幅，f84=成交量，f85=成交额\n    # f46=昨收，f47=今开，f48=最高，f49=最低\n    fields = \"f43,f44,f170,f84,f85,f46,f47,f48,f49\"\n    url = f\"https://push2.eastmoney.com/api/qt/stock/get?fltt=2&invt=2&fields={fields}&secid={secid}\"\n    \n    try:\n        response = requests.get(url, timeout=5)\n        response.raise_for_status()\n        data = response.json()\n        \n        if data.get('data'):\n            item = data['data']\n            price = item.get('f43', 0)\n            change_amt = item.get('f44', 0)\n            change_pct = item.get('f170', 0)\n            pre_close = item.get('f46', 0)\n            open_price = item.get('f47', 0)\n            high = item.get('f48', 0)\n            low = item.get('f49', 0)\n            volume = item.get('f84', 0)\n            amount = item.get('f85', 0)\n            \n            # 清理代码格式\n            clean_code = code.split('.')[0] if '.' in code else code\n            clean_code = clean_code.replace('.HK', '')\n            \n            line = f\"{clean_code},{name},{price:.2f},{change_amt:.2f},{change_pct:.2f},{pre_close:.2f},{open_price:.2f},{high:.2f},{low:.2f},{volume},{amount},{current_time}\"\n            output_lines.append(line)\n            print(f\"✓ {code}: ¥{price:.2f} ({change_pct:+.2f}%)\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"✗ {code}: 无数据\")\n            \n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"✗ {code}: {e}\")\n\n# 保存到 realtime-data.txt\noutput_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt')\nwith open(output_path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write('\\n'.join(output_lines))\n\nprint(f\"\\n数据已保存到：{output_path}\")\nprint(f\"共 {len(output_lines) - 1} 条数据\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125130526}}
{"type":"message","id":"432d27f0","parentId":"a844cb00","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:33.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the setup better. Let me execute the task step by step:\n\n1. First check if market is open (using check_market_status.py)\n2. Clear realtime-data.txt\n3. Get fresh real-time data\n4. Filter based on alert rules\n5. Send alerts via feishu\n\nLet me start by checking market status and then proceed with the workflow. I'll use the existing scripts where possible.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b5905c4dd5594defa489b86f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock && python3 check_market_status.py 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773125130527}}
{"type":"message","id":"ddc3fa90","parentId":"432d27f0","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:33.615Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b5905c4dd5594defa489b86f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"check_market_status.py\", line 28, in <module>\n    cal_df = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=today, end_date=today, is_open='1')\n  File \"/home/openclaw/.local/lib/python3.6/site-packages/tushare/pro/client.py\", line 45, in query\n    raise Exception(result['msg'])\nException: 您的token不对，请确认。\nToken: d5dffac476...ddf85bc33d\n检查交易日历：20260310\n检查交易日历出错：您的token不对，请确认。\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":453,"aggregated":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"check_market_status.py\", line 28, in <module>\n    cal_df = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=today, end_date=today, is_open='1')\n  File \"/home/openclaw/.local/lib/python3.6/site-packages/tushare/pro/client.py\", line 45, in query\n    raise Exception(result['msg'])\nException: 您的token不对，请确认。\nToken: d5dffac476...ddf85bc33d\n检查交易日历：20260310\n检查交易日历出错：您的token不对，请确认。\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125133613}}
{"type":"message","id":"b799c623","parentId":"ddc3fa90","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:36.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TUSHARE_TOKEN seems to be invalid. Let me check if there's an alternative approach. Looking at the get_realtime_data.py script, it uses Eastmoney API which doesn't require a token. Let me use that approach instead, or check if there's a valid token stored elsewhere.\n\nLet me also check the filter_alerts.py script to understand how filtering works.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_99b8ae32a36e48189e86fa6e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/filter_alerts.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dc6b1a88ff6c4c4c95f4b8bd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"TUSHARE_TOKEN\" ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/ 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773125133615}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e74f199","parentId":"b799c623","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:45:36.854Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_99b8ae32a36e48189e86fa6e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n根据预警规则过滤实时数据，生成预警通知\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 预警规则\n# 通用规则：\n# - 下跌 > 3% → 触发\n# - 上涨 > 5% → 触发\n# 中国石油 (601857) 专属规则：\n# - 涨幅 > 2% → 触发\n# - 跌幅 > 1% → 触发\n\ndef check_alert(code, name, change_pct):\n    \"\"\"检查是否触发预警\"\"\"\n    # 中国石油专属规则\n    if code == '601857' or name == '中国石油':\n        if change_pct > 2:\n            return True, '🟢 涨幅 > 2%'\n        elif change_pct < -1:\n            return True, '🔴 跌幅 > 1%'\n    else:\n        # 通用规则\n        if change_pct < -3:\n            return True, '📉 下跌 > 3%'\n        elif change_pct > 5:\n            return True, '📈 上涨 > 5%'\n    \n    return False, None\n\n# 读取实时数据\ndata_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt')\nalerts = []\n\ntry:\n    with open(data_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        lines = f.readlines()\n    \n    if len(lines) < 2:\n        print(\"数据文件为空或格式错误\")\n        sys.exit(0)\n    \n    # 解析数据（跳过表头）\n    for line in lines[1:]:\n        line = line.strip()\n        if not line:\n            continue\n        \n        parts = line.split(',')\n        if len(parts) < 6:\n            continue\n        \n        code = parts[0]\n        name = parts[1]\n        price = float(parts[2])\n        change_amt = float(parts[3])\n        change_pct = float(parts[4])\n        time_str = parts[-1] if len(parts) > 10 else datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n        \n        # 检查是否触发预警\n        triggered, rule = check_alert(code, name, change_pct)\n        if triggered:\n            alerts.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'name': name,\n                'price': price,\n                'change_amt': change_amt,\n                'change_pct': change_pct,\n                'time': time_str,\n                'rule': rule\n            })\n            print(f\"⚠️ {code} {name}: ¥{price:.2f} ({change_pct:+.2f}%) - {rule}\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n共触发 {len(alerts)} 条预警\")\n    \n    if not alerts:\n        print(\"无预警信息，结束任务\")\n        sys.exit(0)\n    \n    # 按涨跌幅排序（绝对值大的在前）\n    alerts.sort(key=lambda x: abs(x['change_pct']), reverse=True)\n    \n    # 生成预警消息（表格格式）\n    message_lines = [\n        \"⚠️ 股价预警通知\",\n        \"\",\n        \"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 |\",\n        \"|------|------|--------|--------|-------|\"\n    ]\n    \n    for alert in alerts:\n        sign = '+' if alert['change_pct'] > 0 else ''\n        amt_sign = '+' if alert['change_amt'] > 0 else ''\n        message_lines.append(\n            f\"| {alert['code']} | {alert['name']} | ¥{alert['price']:.2f} | {sign}{alert['change_pct']:.2f}% | {amt_sign}{alert['change_amt']:.2f} |\"\n        )\n    \n    message_lines.extend([\n        \"\",\n        \"⚙️ 预警规则\",\n        \"• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\",\n        \"• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\",\n        \"• 中国石油专属：🟢 涨幅 > 2% | 🔴 跌幅 > 1%\",\n        \"\",\n        f\"📊 数据时间：{alerts[0]['time']}\"\n    ])\n    \n    message = '\\n'.join(message_lines)\n    \n    # 保存预警消息\n    alert_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-message.txt')\n    with open(alert_path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(message)\n    \n    print(f\"\\n预警消息已保存到：{alert_path}\")\n    print(\"\\n\" + message)\n    \nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"处理数据出错：{e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n    sys.exit(1)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773125136849}}
