{"type":"message","id":"cbf10dfb","parentId":"5006c31b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:46:06.642Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the data format is slightly different from what filter_alerts.py expects. The filter script expects:\n- code, name, price, change_amt, change_pct, ...time\n\nBut the current data has:\n- 代码，名称，当前价，涨跌额，涨跌幅，昨收，今开，最高，最低，成交量，成交额，时间\n\nThe columns are:\n- 代码 (code)\n- 名称 (name)\n- 当前价 (price)\n- 涨跌额 (change_amt) - but the values look wrong (12.30 for 中国石油?)\n- 涨跌幅 (change_pct) - but the values look like percentages (-7.28)\n\nWait, looking at the data more carefully:\n- 中国石油: 当前价=11.98, 涨跌额=12.30, 涨跌幅=-7.28\n\nThe 涨跌额 (change amount) of 12.30 doesn't make sense if the price is 11.98. This seems like the API returned different fields than expected.\n\nLet me look at the get_realtime_data.py script again - it seems like the fields mapping might be off. But the 涨跌幅 (-7.28%) looks correct.\n\nActually, looking at the Eastmoney API response, the fields might be mapped differently. Let me check the filter_alerts.py script to see how it parses the data and adjust accordingly.\n\nThe filter script expects CSV with comma separator and parses:\n- parts[0] = code\n- parts[1] = name\n- parts[2] = price\n- parts[3] = change_amt\n- parts[4] = change_pct\n\nBut the current file has:\n- parts[0] = 代码 (header) or 601857\n- parts[1] = 名称 or 中国石油\n- parts[2] = 当前价 or 11.98\n- parts[3] = 涨跌额 or 12.30 (this seems wrong)\n- parts[4] = 涨跌幅 or -7.28\n\nThe change_pct is at parts[4] which is -7.28, which looks correct as a percentage.\n\nLet me run the filter script and see what happens. But first, I need to update the filter script to handle the header correctly (it has Chinese headers now).\n\nActually, looking at the filter_alerts.py, it skips the header line (lines[1:]), so that should be fine. The issue is that the change_pct is at index 4, which the script reads correctly.\n\nLet me run the filter script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_adb1e9e72d3e43479a797981","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock && python3 filter_alerts.py 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773125154602}}
